author: @marimartinez9651
text:
Congratulations to the 1st Bluedragon (Blue Dragon/BSA) Series Awards 2022 recipient, Mr. Kim Jongin aka KAI, who was awarded the Best (Rookie) Male Entertainer Award, for his part in the Netflix reality series, "New World." 
He's a humble, unique individual of many talents.
Very well-deserved.
We love to see it. 
He's thriving in various fields & not just in music.
May he continue to live a beautiful, wonderful life full of good health, happiness, love, & many blessings. 
#KAI #카이 #NewWorldStarKAI #BlueDragonSeriesAwards #BlueDragonSeriesAwards2022

text: Kai fue reclutado el 2007 por SM Entertaiment en el  por su manera de bailar e incluso ganó un premio de popularidad en el mismo concurso. En el colegio elemental (2º grado), empezó a aprender a bailar jazz y ballet. Comenzó a soñar con ser un bailarín de ballet, pero tras ver bailar a Shinhwa, decidió convertirse en cantante. Hizo su audición en el colegio elemental (6º grado) pero le dijeron que volviera dos años más tarde por que era demasiado joven.

author: @tamararioja
text: For those who come and comment that "we all came to see the tik tok dancer", I have to get them out of their grave mistake. Most of us come to enjoy the talent of KAI, because for nine years he has demonstrated and has been considered the best kpop dancer. He now debuts with his album and turns out to break records, he's nominated for best album in just 9 days of debut! Most of us come to celebrate the power of kpop, and specifically the power of KAI. The dancers are not only beautiful, but also talented, it is a shame that these people do not say so, they only talk about their beauty (that shows poor understanding and superficiality). What is more sad, is that those people (few) assume that most of us come to see if the girls are pretty or not (they don't even realize that the number of comments praising KAI is much higher)! . 32 million mv views in just one month, idol statements about how amazing and talented Kai is, and nine-year awards to EXO speak to what we all know: KAI is a god of dance !! Conclusion: Most of us came to see KAI. Sorry kids. You are welcome to watch the girls all you like, but don't assume nonsense :), it's embarrassing for you.

레전더 리 그룹 EXO를 갖게되어 정말 축복 받았습니다. 개인적으로 정말 열심히 일하기 때문입니다. 엑소의 모든 멤버는 매우 잘 생기고 재능이 있습니다. 모든 EXO 멤버들은 비주얼, 안무, 보컬에 딱 맞는 매우 강력한 보이스입니다. 엑소 전 멤버 베스트 보컬 베스트 댄서 베스트 비주얼

author: @haidahnovianti4086
text:
Dear my family EXO-L,

EXO-L, soon 2020 will end. I want to say thank you for still being here with EXO. We all know that 2020 is not an easy year for everyone, especially EXO-L. Thank you for always holding hands until the end of this year. Thank you for always supporting and loving our 9 peterpan. I really want to say that I love you forever. If I could say I love you every day, every second, every minute, I'd say it. 

Once again, I am very grateful and very much in love with you. I never regret ever knowing EXO and joining all of you EXO-L. Y'all accompany, comfort, and take good care of me this year. Let's stay together for a long time!!

EXO-L, WISH YOU A MERRY CHRISTMAS!! HAPPY NEW YEAR!

Love from Indonesia.
